                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/9ae11dc0f2551b8b7f40e04339c04cf8_6060284260064264758.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Yaoyao",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ได้รับชัยชนะภายใน 6 เทิร์น",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4369,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/c455da7fd161e1cdb81d360bef8262fd_8211657757015468283.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Beneficent",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ชนะโดยจำนวนตัวละครที่ถูกกำจัดต่ำกว่า 2 ตัว",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4369,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/c455da7fd161e1cdb81d360bef8262fd_8211657757015468283.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Beneficent",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "การต่อสู้อย่างจริงจัง",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "แนะนำด่าน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"ว้าววว มีวิธีเล่นหลายแบบเลย... บางทีถ้าเล่นหลาย ๆ ตา Yaoyao ก็อาจจะช่ำชองก็ได้นะ แถมจะได้ไปแนะนำเกมการ์ดนี้ให้อาจารย์ด้วย!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "[กฎพิเศษ] ในตอนเริ่ม \"Yaoyao\" จะติดตั้งการ์ดพรสวรรค์ \"Beneficent\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ทีมของคู่ต่อสู้",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4366,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/9ae11dc0f2551b8b7f40e04339c04cf8_6060284260064264758.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Yaoyao",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3183,
